pageTitle: Caramelized Black Walnuts at The Vermont Country Store
textBeforeTable: Nutrition Shelf Life: 1 year Specifications Item is Kosher - Approved by OU Sugar, Black Walnuts, Honey, Butter, Salt and Soy Lecithin Ingredients Allergy information: contains black walnuts, milk and soy ingredients. manufactured on equipment that processes products containing peanuts, tree nuts, dairy products, soy and wheat. Safety Warnings Caramelized Black Walnuts Carmelized black walnuts are a sweet, nutty, and healthy treat all in one. Excellent source of omega-3 fatty acids Caramelized using pure cane sugar Black walnuts roasted in copper kettles Sure we could tell you that black walnuts are an excellent source of omega-3 fatty acids, protein, and fiber. Or that these wild black walnuts are hand-harvested in the American heartland and then slowly roasted in copper kettles and caramelized using pure cane sugar. But, if you’re like us, once you taste their rich, earthy nuttiness and complementing sweetness, that’s all the convincing you’ll need to make these tasty treats your own. Great for snacking or adding to salads. 8 oz. bag.
